@NotesApp.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7014

### Register
POST {{NotesApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
POST {{NotesApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Current user (requires auth cookie from register/login)
GET {{NotesApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me

### Logout (requires auth cookie)
POST {{NotesApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout

### List notes (requires auth cookie)
GET {{NotesApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/notes

### Create note (requires auth cookie)
POST {{NotesApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My first note",
  "body": "Hello from the notes API."
}

### Create note — validation error (empty title)
POST {{NotesApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "   ",
  "body": "Body only"
}

### Notes without auth — expect 401
GET {{NotesApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/notes
